Lloyds Says Leitch to Step Down as Scottish Widows Chairman

-- B y   E d w a r d   E v a n s
-- 
2011-09-19T06:16:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/lloyds-says-leitch-to-step-down-as-scottish-widows-chairman.html
Lloyds Banking Group said Lord
Leitch will step down as chairman of its Scottish Widows unit at
the end of 2011 because of “increasing time pressure from his
other business commitments.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Edward Evans at 
 eevans3@bloomberg.net  